name: Viraj Ramakrishnan
details: Hi! I'm Viraj and welcome to my bio! I love many things: math, teaching, languages, listening to music, guitar, singing, running, tennis, cooking, and, (who could forget) CSM. In my spare time you'll catch me trying to find the best Thai restaurant in Berkeley, sermonizing to anyone who will listen about the dread of impending graduation, or making CSM acronyms with considerable sentence mangling. Above everything i love learning and I'd love to learn about you! If you see me, approach me and ask to play a game of set, I will not refuse.
